page.title: 19BILSDALE STUDY GROUP.
page.content: The subjects of the indoor meetings have been;Buildings in cleveland, Stonewalls & Standing Stones, Maps & their uses, Old Recipes & Remedies, Limekilns,Jet & Ironstone mining, Tracing Family History,Old Haggs of Bilsdale (A Woodland History) Spout House, Video & Architectural Photographs, Reminiscences of Chop Gate School,Landscape Photography Early Bilsdale,Old Photographs & Postcards,Flora & Fauna. The Outings hve included:Hagg House, appreciating landscape,Ryedale Folk Museum,Birch Wood,Wethercote,Garfit William Beck,Laskill,Bridestones, Tripsdale,Cablestones and a visit to the Jorvik Museum York.
